{"tid":668378,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"以RSA實現連登嘅pm功能","createTime":"2018-05-17T14:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T13:23:21.000Z","uid":34301,"like":43,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dffbf9aadbd0bcdcee4acd23c439ed3b3e584a4a","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"鑑於連登無pm功能<br />\n而知道大家又咁注重私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟希望透過呢個機會同大家分享下點喺連登裡面用RSA嚟幫大家嘅信息加密<br />\n為咗方便大家了解RSA點運作<br />\n我會用呢個網站幫手解釋<br />\n<a href=\"http://travistidwell.com/jsencrypt/demo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravistidwell.com%2Fjsencrypt%2Fdemo%2F&d=CjZ%2F%2FeBCvDBHkUoqNCXKLosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=8668e271\" target=\"_blank\">http://travistidwell.com/jsencrypt/demo/</a><br />\n<br />\n接住落嚟我將會解答以下呢幾條問題<br />\n1. 咩嘢係RSA？<br />\n2. 點利用RSA幫助加密信息？<br />\n3. 點解要喺度用RSA？<br />\n4. RSA可以幫助實現咩功能？<br />\n5. 可以點喺連登裡面用RSA幫助加密信息？<br />\n<br />\n我無讀過密碼學，所以理論嘢留返畀其他有讀過密碼學嘅人答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddba6012c0842fd9ebde8c0b8d29dfee871dd15","tid":668378,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55127e0ff051984a548520fe9f285c2a7a1c9590","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:40:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 咩嘢係RSA？</span></span><br />\nRSA係一種非對稱加密算法<br />\n簡單而言就係你每一次想要一個新身份<br />\n你將會因應唔同 密鑰長度(Key size) 而獲分兩條以文本形式呈現嘅 密鑰(Key)<br />\n短啲嗰條叫 公鑰(Public key)，顧名思義就係周街都可以知<br />\n長啲嗰條叫 私鑰(Private key)，顧名思義就係只可以得你/授權人士知<br />\nRSA允許你由私鑰得出公鑰，但係唔可以由公鑰得出私鑰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">注意：密鑰長度1024位元以下嘅RSA加密算法已經唔安全，所以鼓勵大家起碼都要用1024</span><br />\n<br />\n以密鑰長度為512位元為例（雖然唔安全，但係作為例子嚟講勝在夠短），其中一個例子嘅私鑰會係咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----<br />\nMIIBOAIBAAJAfLAdi/1ZPCWsr4WvzmxXvnR8nUibCDGVRxc4guX8MTOWFUH5/bYe<br />\nisOBZ9CfI6k22zH5nEnntL4Ov/8Ikt0uAQIDAQABAkBYLYhHttxDf/U2j9l7pv0K<br />\ncICsDmutCLuj8dUCJTkLZYMJ1bK4fAyNuMdBtAleekRFhvME2aCMfUmml9w0uZ0B<br />\nAiEA8Fi0NZEqJOmAIjI782w12zZki+7kJCCQXBMP1UvshVECIQCEzwl7DyfmMwiK<br />\natkmvs3yEsIwxS8Sts56CDxgX6ixsQIgcx4pgpa7Ft74Tmi9KkSkLxEIa7XKdDtc<br />\nqZ0/siwhZ2ECIEguSkXSx+mqRPMN/XW8cCwoG9jr4pi2OGREw6PRedsRAiAVKH6W<br />\nkedUMtfYKLGbqJWWBI0+/h5SQ/xsokR9hrH1fA==<br />\n-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----</span><br />\n<br />\n而呢條私鑰相對應嘅公鑰會係咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----<br />\nMFswDQYJKoZIhvcNAQEBBQADSgAwRwJAfLAdi/1ZPCWsr4WvzmxXvnR8nUibCDGV<br />\nRxc4guX8MTOWFUH5/bYeisOBZ9CfI6k22zH5nEnntL4Ov/8Ikt0uAQIDAQAB<br />\n-----END PUBLIC KEY-----</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你要加密一篇 明文(Plaintext) 就要使用公鑰<br />\n如果你想解密一篇 密文(Ciphertext) 就要使用私鑰<br />\n<br />\n如果我想加密嘅明文係「中文」<br />\n我就要先用上面條公鑰將佢加密成<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Vz0cb743NXdqTxH0AMx9MEDlp8l3wndvFTAefl6cTeDgeC49NKg4o5KY+wIRH9IxOkS2byDLmvxFchhMpfMhiQ==</span><br />\n<br />\n如果你想解密呢篇密文，就一定只可以用公鑰相對應嘅私鑰解密<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">想試嘅話可以去個網，跟住將&quot;Key Size&quot;設定為&quot;512 bit&quot;，跟住再喺&quot;Private Key&quot;個位貼上上面例子嗰條私鑰，然後喺&quot;Encrypted:&quot;貼上上面條密文再撳&quot;Encrypt / Decrypt&quot;應該就會見到&quot;Text to encrypt:&quot;嗰度出咗「中文」兩隻字</span>"},{"pid":"8f78b58c561abe2713a367642d0e6d910a908a13","tid":668378,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff8368514946a9d7abf727130a8c96541fc2104","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 點利用RSA幫助加密信息？</span></span><br />\n當而家有兩個分別叫Alice同埋Bob嘅人想傾計，佢哋想確保大家嘅信息唔會畀第三者睇到<br />\n假設而家Alice同Bob獲分配嘅(&quot;[Public key]&quot;, &quot;[Private key]&quot;)如下<br />\nAlice:\t(&quot;abc&quot;, &quot;def&quot;)<br />\nBob:\t(&quot;ghi&quot;, &quot;ljk&quot;)<br />\n提提大家，Alice同Bob都知大家嘅公鑰係咩<br />\n<br />\n如果Alice要發一段信息畀Bob，Alice要先用Bob嘅公鑰&quot;ghi&quot;加密段信息，再發送呢段密文畀Bob，Bob就可以用返自己條私鑰&quot;ljk&quot;解密篇密文，從而就可以知道Alice原先段信息係咩啦<br />\n如果Bob想發信息畀Alice都係差唔多，就係用Alice條公鑰&quot;abc&quot;加密段信息，然後將呢段密文發送畀Alice，Alice用返自己條私鑰&quot;def&quot;就可以解密篇密文啦<br />\n<br />\n等我解釋下點解咁樣係可行，如果你只係想Bob呢個人知段信息講乜，你要確保只有Bob呢個人有可以解密呢篇密文嘅密鑰，即係Bob一定要有條私鑰<br />\n但<span style=\"color: orange;\">正正因為RSA嘅設計係<ins>只允許私鑰用嚟解密由佢相對應嘅公鑰所加密嘅密文</ins></span>，所以Alice只可以用Bob條公鑰嚟加密段信息啦，如果唔係Bob就無辦法用私鑰解密啦"},{"pid":"463bb078a6db6ca5fdb2a791b101b3d500fe8a31","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 點解要喺度用RSA？</span></span><br />\n其實無人逼你用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係分享下架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係當你唔肯定某個add你telegram嘅人係咪就係連登搵你嗰個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者你哋唔想交換telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用RSA幫手加密你哋喺連登裡面嘅post其實已經可以當兩個人傾計咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其他人無你哋兩個人嘅私鑰係唔會知你哋講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0c733c2d96d213de8c9d69c9bb6cc7d9b0ca03","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. RSA可以幫助實現咩功能？</span></span><br />\n呢度嘅話我暫時諗到pm同group chat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1996d83ab112c520c82b205a871ef9312481715","tid":668378,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"即係接收PM嗰個掉條4096bit public key 出黎<br />\n<br />\nSend PM嗰個用佢條public key 加密"},{"pid":"07fd83fafc46abe22dc161a47b22824075ba9b6f","tid":668378,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe47d35a60e1bf49b6175dabfe7a2807d71e8f0a","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5. 可以點喺連登裡面用RSA幫助加密信息？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">a) pm</span><br />\npm其實好簡單<br />\n假設兩個連登仔女想傾偈<br />\n大家先打返自己嘅公鑰出嚟<br />\n例如Alice同Bob大家都係連登仔女<br />\nAlice開post先啦，帖文記錄如下<br />\n<br />\nAlice: &quot;abc&quot;<br />\nBob: &quot;ghi&quot;<br />\n<br />\n由呢一步開始大家就可以正式用RSA加密算法幫手加密啲信息<br />\n<br />\nBob: &quot;To Alice: B1rvs6g4U15hT07RUfCV3b9W77BubFGPOmiLGHS3D8unyn/tj3PB5mEMPZIpvvObD9rrKqIXsISa35IElOMl7Q==&quot;<br />\nAlice: &quot;To Bob: ......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n如此類推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">b) group chat</span><br />\n至於group chat呢，假設而家多咗兩個連登仔女叫Cathy同Dick<br />\n同樣大家都要必先張貼自己嘅公鑰<br />\n如果Alice係group admin，佢只係想加Cathy入group，但係唔鍾意Dick<br />\n佢就可以另外整一組新嘅公鑰私鑰組合 e.g. (&quot;111&quot;, &quot;222&quot;)<br />\n用Bob條公鑰加密&quot;222&quot;畀Bob知啦，同埋用Cathy條公鑰加密&quot;222&quot;畀Cathy知啦<br />\n咁Bob同Cathy就可以用返自己條私鑰解密由Alice發畀佢哋嘅信息，咁就會知道群組嘅私鑰係&quot;222&quot;啦<br />\n每當大家溝通嘅時候，就可以用群組嘅公鑰&quot;111&quot;加密段信息，咁群組成員就可以用群組嘅私鑰&quot;222&quot;解密段信息啦"},{"pid":"ad17412facac0cdf98590e620395104aa597a8c9","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1996d83ab112c520c82b205a871ef9312481715","tid":668378,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"即係接收PM嗰個掉條4096bit public key 出黎<br />\n<br />\nSend PM嗰個用佢條public key 加密"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住接收PM嗰個用返自己條private key解密"},{"pid":"7574706d89786be734e0e3d29f5f1a8d970c6435","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"我都估到有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d48d1f1262e9967e9835333dd335f15ebe708fb","tid":668378,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b45735f9f79fe77206cc501e2913e35f4251264","tid":668378,"uid":80153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"欣賞巴打的思路，不過淨講原理唔夠，用咩tool 做先得<br />\n<br />\n真係裝舊OpenSSL 打command 又唔係個個識"},{"pid":"b7cd08abb84b632b1f8a9a948421c80ab9ef0cf3","tid":668378,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b45735f9f79fe77206cc501e2913e35f4251264","tid":668378,"uid":80153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"欣賞巴打的思路，不過淨講原理唔夠，用咩tool 做先得<br />\n<br />\n真係裝舊OpenSSL 打command 又唔係個個識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"057968f3b841decd4754dd32692e141468eb2942","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b45735f9f79fe77206cc501e2913e35f4251264","tid":668378,"uid":80153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"欣賞巴打的思路，不過淨講原理唔夠，用咩tool 做先得<br />\n<br />\n真係裝舊OpenSSL 打command 又唔係個個識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"我其實專登唔講tool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我覺得咁樣如果要依賴其他software (e.g. gnupg, ssh-keygen)又唔係個個識同埋方便用<br />\n如果連仔或者其他admin見到嘅話<br />\n唔想嘥錢整pm系統，不妨考慮下幫每位會員會分配一組public-private key pair或者整個keygen<br />\n咁會員照樣可以有類似pm嘅溝通方式，你哋又可以慳返下啲錢咁囉<br />\n不過如果你哋注重討論質素同埋驚有太多小圈子/狗公咁就另計啦"},{"pid":"429f57189fe6f25d3f98b46283b3bdca0cfca4e0","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7cd08abb84b632b1f8a9a948421c80ab9ef0cf3","tid":668378,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b45735f9f79fe77206cc501e2913e35f4251264","tid":668378,"uid":80153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"欣賞巴打的思路，不過淨講原理唔夠，用咩tool 做先得<br />\n<br />\n真係裝舊OpenSSL 打command 又唔係個個識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"agger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:01:43.000Z","msg":"btw 其實我都係拎返啲舊嘅原理同大家分享下<br />\n希望大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5709005752353bf023d5501a72210a7729928e","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f17ba4bce35d757d15052accc596e0e4a8ad9b6","tid":668378,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a15f16c909075645850fe185c6c0860eeab659f","tid":668378,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1